overview: Teen Riley Reid calls personal trainer Lana Rhoades to get her body ready for college. They agree to start with yoga and meet at the park. Riley agrees to go topless for the session. Lana caresses her small breasts and tells her she can work on her chest muscles. She cops a feel of her tight ass when she makes her do pushups. Nia Nacci found a cell phone on the street and is going through it in order to find its owner. When she decides to go through the photos, she can't believe how hot the owner actually is. Kristen Scott is in the school library writing in her diary. She's expressing her love for Elsa Jean through poetry and prose. When Elsa walks into the library Kristen freaks out. When she gets up to leave the girls collide into each other dropping all their school books in the process.
title: Under Her Spell
